├─ Oil Production: 980 bbl/day (severely depleted)
├─ Water Cut: 44.2%
├─ Pressure: 2,310 psi
├─ Issue: Mechanical failure indicated by water production spike
├─ Recommendation: Pull rod string; inspect for corrosion; consider ESP retrofit
└─ Estimated Impact: +350 bbl/day recovery = $4.6M/year revenue

